2. Video
    a. To define video stream interfaces
    b. To add video device enumulation for iOS & Android.
    c. To add render implemention for iOS & Android.
    d. To add video codec(parameters) enumulation: vp8.

3. Interaces
    a. To provide native clang interfaces for iOS.
    b. To provide jni interfaces for Android.


